title: Bryant McFadden Chargers/Chiefs insanity + NFL Week 15 Picks with Pete Prisco/RJ White (Football 12/14)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Bryant McFadden to break down the wild game between the Chargers and the Chiefs from Thursday Night Football before being joined by Pete Prisco and R.J. White to break down every game against the spread for Week 15 of the NFL season.
